{"ID":270319, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"319\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs318.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs320.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 319<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">oil unto me throughout your generations.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> Also Exodus 40 Chap., 15 v.&mdash;&ldquo;And thou shalt anoint\n  them as thou didst anoint their father (Aaron) that they may minister unto me in the priest&rsquo;s office;\n  for their anointing shall surely be an everlasting Priesthood throughout their generations.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Here is a little of law which must be fulfilled. The Levitical Priesthood is forever\n  hereditary<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span>&mdash;fixed on the head of Aaron and his sons forever,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> and was in active operation down to\n  Zacharias<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> the father of John. Zacharias would have had no child had not God given him a son. He\n  sent his angel to declare unto Zacharias that his wife Elizabeth should bear him a son, whose name\n  was to be called John.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The keys of the Aaronic Priesthood were committed unto him, and he was as the voice of one\n  crying in the wilderness saying: &ldquo;Prepare ye the way of the Lord and make his paths straight.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Kingdom of heaven suffereth violence,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> etc.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The kingdom of heaven continueth in authority until John.<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The authority taketh it by absolute power.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">John having the power took the Kingdom by authority.<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">How have you obtained all this great knowledge? By the gift of the Holy Ghost.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Wrested the Kingdom from the Jews.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Of these stony Gentiles&mdash;these dogs&mdash;to raise up children unto Abraham.<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Savior said unto John, I must be baptized by you. Why so? To fulfil all righteousness.<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span>\n  John refuses at first, but afterwards obeyed by administering the ordinance of baptism unto him,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>\n  Jesus having no other legal administrator to apply to.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">There is no salvation between the two lids of the Bible without a legal administrator. Jesus was\n  then the legal administrator, and ordained His Apostles.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span>&mdash;MSS. Historian&rsquo;s Office.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">The Prophet&rsquo;s Remarks at the Funeral of Judge Higbee<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Brethren and Sisters, you will find these words in 2 Peter 3:10, 11:&mdash;&ldquo;But the day of the Lord\n  will come as a thief in the night; in the which the heavens shall pass away with a great noise, and\n  the elements shall melt with fervent heat, the earth also and the works that are therein shall be\n  burned up.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106192\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106192)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106192)\">Ex. 30:30-31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106220\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106220)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106220)\">Ex. 40:15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108396\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108396)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108396)\">Luke 1:5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114318\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114318)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114318)\">D&amp;C 68:20-21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114628\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114628)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114628)\">D&amp;C 84:18,27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115411\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115411)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115411)\">D&amp;C 107:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108397\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108397)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108397)\">Luke 1:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108399\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108399)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108399)\">Luke 1:5-13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113468\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113468)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113468)\">D&amp;C 27:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107166\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107166)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107166)\">Isa. 40:3<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108299\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108299)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108299)\">Mark 1:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107946\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107946)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107946)\">Matt. 11:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114671\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114671)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114671)\">D&amp;C 84:27<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114680\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114680)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114680)\">D&amp;C 84:28<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108141\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108141)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108141)\">Matt. 21:24-25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115765\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115765)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115765)\">D&amp;C 121:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107776\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107776)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107776)\">Matt. 3:7-12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107777\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107777)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107777)\">Matt. 3:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107786\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107786)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107786)\">Matt. 3:13-15<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107794\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107794)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107794)\">Matt. 3:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108837\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108837)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108837)\">John 15:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}